details: From the classic American muscle car to modern race marvels, Big Time Muscle die-cast vehicles by Jada Toys brings the best of American muscle car culture to a smaller scale. These vehicles feature traditionally themed paint jobs, highly stylized wheels, detailed engine bay, and are ready to tear up the road. These beautifully sculpted collectible vehicles are sure to be a standout in any die-cast collection! Collect them all!
